ActFirst Nations Goods and Services Tax Act
SubjectOrder Amending Schedule 1 to the First Nations Goods and Services Tax Act, No. 2015–1 (Aitchelitz, Kwaw-kwaw-Apilt and Skowkale)
PrecisOrder Amending SCHEDULE 1 TO THE FIRST NATIONS GOODS AND SERVICES TAX ACT, NO. 2015-1 (AITCHELITZ, KWAW-KWAW-APILT AND SKOWKALE) in order to enable the three Indian bands, with the agreement of the Government of Canada, to implement the First Nations Goods and Services Tax within their respective lands.
